data.name: lblLength.ToolTip
data.value:
dna > code length (shortcut pattern)
tip: -the amount of characters after 'dna >' -shortcut for running proceeding algorithm
example: dna > test length = 4 tes. = 4 test1 = 5
right click: options double click: edit

data.name: ListBox1.ToolTip
data.value: right click: show database menu ctrl + right click: clear text, db menu ctrl + double click: more db options ctrl + e: selected db item to text ctrl + space: db menu double click or enter: run selected item delete: delete item escape + insert: test selected item long hold f5 then release: run / test item ctrl + c: copy selected item ctrl + mouse wheel: adjust font size f1: show database item tip pinch to zoom

data.name: txtString.ToolTip
data.value: 'help' + enter: view manual (f1: toggle tips) double click blank text box: get dna > 'code' right click or ctrl + space: editor menu ctrl + right click or right click hold + move: db menu hold or tap pause break key: abort algorithm ctrl + mouse wheel: adjust font size pinch to zoom (touch-screen) left ctrl + enter or mouse middle click: print '«»' ctrl + left click: repeat last clicked item from menu ctrl + s: save text to database / db ctrl + e: edit (text -> db selected item) ctrl + u: update (save text -> db selected item) ctrl + f: find selected text in db escape + insert or right control + enter: test / run long hold f5 then release: run selected text long hold right click + move: run selected text 'exit' + enter: close program
